<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>هـ ل ب<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c4">[٥٤٣٥ - هـ ل ب]</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>هلَّبَ يهلِّب، تهليبًا، فهو مُهلِّب، والمفعول مُهلَّب<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">• هلَّبَ القومَ بلسانه:</span> هلَبهم، هجاهم وشتمهم.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c5">• هلَّب شَعْرَه:</span> نتفَه.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>